with A as (
select
  t1.id,
  t1.report_id,
  t1.creator_id,
  t1.create_time,
  t1.action,
  t1.platform,
  t3.nick,
  t4.ip,
  t4.ua,
  t2.project_id,
  t2.title,
  t5.id as folder_id,
  t5.name as folder_name,
  t5.root_id as root_folder_id,
  t5.root_name as root_folder_name 
  from (
    select
      id,
      report_id,
      creator_id,
      create_time,
      action,
      platform
    from
      youdata_report_recent_visit where day='${start_day}'
  ) t1 
  left join youdata_new_report t2 on t1.report_id = t2.id
  left join youdata_bigviz_user t3 on t1.creator_id = t3.id
  left join youdata_login_logout_event t4 on t1.creator_id = t4.user_id and t4.create_time <= t1.create_time
  left join youdata_temp_folder t5 on t2.folder_id = t5.id
)
insert overwrite table youdata_all_operation_report partition (day='${start_day}')
 select
  id,
  report_id,
  creator_id,
  create_time,
  action,
  platform,
  nick,
  ip,
  ua,
  project_id,
  title,
  folder_id,
  folder_name,
  root_folder_id,
  root_folder_name
    from
      (
        select
          b.*,
          row_number() over(
            partition by id
            order by
              create_time desc
          ) as rn
        from
          A as b
      ) a
    where
      rn = 1
